review:
A pretty buggy hidden object game:

- items in hidden object scenes will every once in a while refuse to actually be selected, but I have always successfully got them after a few clicks;
- some of the minigames are really buggy and the skip button location just begs you to accidentally click it;
- on top of the bugs with them quite a lot of are really tedious to complete for no good reason and otherwise really easy.

Works without issues with Proton (7.0-4).
